### ==========================================

### Health
GET http://localhost:8090/health

### Supported Languages (public)
GET http://localhost:8090/api/v1/languages

### Transcribe (stub)
POST http://localhost:8090/api/v1/voice/transcribe
Authorization: Bearer {{residentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"audio_base64": "dGVzdA==", "source_language": "hi"}

### ==========================================
