### Health
GET http://localhost:8089/health

### ==========================================
### ERROR CASES
### ==========================================

### No token → 401
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/complaints

### Invalid token → 401
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/complaints
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token

### Resident trying admin endpoint → 403
POST http://localhost:8084/api/v1/payments/generate-bills
Authorization: Bearer {{residentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"month": "2026-04"}
